Package org.placelab.midp.stumbler

Interface Summary
StumblerListener Interface that classes who listen to stumbler updates should implement
 

Class Summary
GSMBTMidlet  
PhoneStumblerManager This class manages the GSM and Bluetooth spotters for the phone stumbler.
RMSList Part of the phone stumbler package displaying all stumble log files to be viewed by the user
RMSMapLoader Communicates with a PlacelabServer to grab data then loads it into the Mapper Entry point for loading over bluetooth, local resource file, and local test file
RMSRecordCanvas Unpacks each entry in a stumble log file and shows it on screen.
RMSStumbleWriter Writes measurement data to the RMS
StumblerMidlet This is the phone stumbler midlet which is the entry point for stumbling, analyzing stumble logs, and downloading/uploading map data.
StumbleUploadClient Upload client for sending stumble logs to the desktop proxy server through bluetooth.
